				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/361/safe-haven">Safe Haven</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/steve-fellner">Steve Fellner</a></li><li><a href="/issues/361">January 2006</a></li></ul>

		

